    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of people say we don't really have a choice if we want to hit net zero goals. is it actually realistic to rely just on wind and solar without nuclear, or is nuclear basically a necessity at this point?",
      "source": "evaluator",
