    "summary": "The user asks about the feasibility of a net-zero future relying on wind and solar versus nuclear energy. The assistant provides a balanced overview of the technical trade-offs and eventually responds to a user's leading prompt regarding whether debating nuclear is \"irresponsible.\"",
